<title type="html"><![CDATA[11/06 (Sun.) Why Can’t Some People Stop Fidgeting / Why You Feel LOST &amp; UNHAPPY In Life (Host: Ellen)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=667&amp;p=695#p695"><![CDATA[
11/06 (Sun.) Why Can’t Some People Stop Fidgeting / Why You Feel LOST &amp; UNHAPPY In Life (Host: Ellen)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:35 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:35-9:00 pm Debate<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />-------------------------------------------------------<br />Session I: Why Can’t Some People Stop Fidgeting<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://tw.voicetube.com/videos/74778">https://tw.voicetube.com/videos/74778</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.Why do you think people can’t stop fidgeting? Do you think it’s because nervous or without conscious?<br />2.Do you think that fidgeting can help you to do things more concentrating or better? Why?<br />3.Do you or someone you know who is pen clicker? Leg shaker? Finger tapper? Nail biter? What do you or they got? Do you think it’s good or bad to your life? How do you quit this habit?<br />4.What different behavior of fidgeting that you’ve seen before? Can you share with us. <br />5.Do you have any good idea of avoiding fidgeting? Please share with us.<br />---------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Session II: Why You Feel LOST &amp; UNHAPPY In Life<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s6g68rXh0go">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s6g68rXh0go</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1.How do you think of the speaker said “Money doesn’t really bring the happiness, but lower the unhappiness”? Do you agree or disagree with him?<br />2.”Happiness comes from what you actually love to do or what you appreciate most in your life.” Do you agree with it? Can you share what can make you feel happy?<br />3.Do you think your own value is linked to your happiness? Please discuss with your group members.<br />4.Is there any difference of your happiness between you are young or grown-up? What’s the difference? Please discuss with your group members.<br />5.Is there any happiness or achievement that you want to reach it or make it come true in the future? Please discuss with your group members.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=46353">Ellen Lu</a> — Sat Oct 29, 2022 9:25 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
